" height=\"5\" rx=\"1\"/><rect x=\"9\" y=\"10\" width=\"5\" height=\"5\" rx=\"1\"/></svg>\n        <span>Test catalog</span>\n        <span class=\"nav-num\">04</span>\n      </button>\n      <button class=\"nav\" data-view=\"about\" type=\"button\">\n        <svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6.2\"/><path d=\"M8 7.2v4M8 5.2v.05\"/></svg>\n        <span>About</span>\n        <span class=\"nav-num\">05</span>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"sidebar-foot\">\n        <div class=\"hint\">Test suite for issuers &amp; verifiers implementing <strong>OID4VCI 1.0 Final</strong> and <strong>OID4VP 1.0 Final</strong>.</div>\n      </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"content\" aria-live=\"polite\">\n      <!-- RUN VIEW -->\n      <article class=\"view active\" id=\"view-run\" aria-labelledby=\"run-h\">\n        <header class=\"view-header\">\n          <div>\n            <span class=\"eyebrow\">Step 01 · Run</span>\n            <h2 id=\"run-h\">Run a conformance <em>pass.</em></h2>\n            <p>Pick a cross-mode and a target. The webapp dispatches the catalog of test cases against it (or the in-process mock if no target is set) and produces a downloadable report.</p>\n          </div>\n          <span class=\"meta\" id=\"run-meta\">No run yet</span>\n        </header>\n\n        <div class=\"section-title\">Cross-modes <em>— pick one</em></div>\n        <div class=\"cards\" id=\"mode-cards\">\n          <button class=\"card mode\" data-mode=\"I->W\" type=\"button\" style=\"--stagger:60ms\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M2 14V6l7-3 7 3v8\"/><path d=\"M2 14h14\"/><path d=\"M6 14v-4h6v4\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"card-no\">01 · I→W</span>\n            <h3>Issuer <em>→</em> Wallet</h3>\n            <p>Drive a <em>target Issuer</em> with our wallet simulator. Use this to verify an Issuer you control.</p>\n            <div class=\"card-meta\"><span class=\"badge\"><span class=\"dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span data-test-count=\"I->W\">— tests</span></span></div>\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"card mode\" data-mode=\"V->W\" type=\"button\" style=\"--stagger:120ms\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><circle cx=\"7.5\" cy=\"7.5\" r=\"4.5\"/><path d=\"M11 11l4 4\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"card-no\">02 · V→W</span>\n            <h3>Verifier <em>→</em> Wallet</h3>\n            <p>Drive a <em>target Verifier</em> with our wallet simulator. Use this to verify a Verifier you control.</p>\n            <div class=\"card-meta\"><span class=\"badge\"><span class=\"dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span data-test-count=\"V->W\">— tests</span></span></div>\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"card mode selected\" data-mode=\"W->I\" type=\"button\" style=\"--stagger:180ms\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"2\" width=\"9\" height=\"14\" rx=\"1.6\"/><path d=\"M5 5h5M5 8h5M5 11h3\"/><path d=\"M14 9v6\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"card-no\">03 · W→I</span>\n            <h3>Wallet <em>→</em> Issuer</h3>\n            <p>Drive our wallet simulator with a <em>target Issuer</em>. Use this to test a wallet against a real Issuer.</p>\n            <div class=\"card-meta\"><span class=\"badge gold\"><span class=\"dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span data-test-count=\"W->I\">— tests</span></span></div>\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"card mode\" data-mode=\"W->V\" type=\"button\" style=\"--stagger:240ms\">\n            <div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"3\" width=\"14\" height=\"9\" rx=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M5 15h8\"/><path d=\"M2 12h14\"/></svg>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"card-no\">04 · W→V</span>\n            <h3>Wallet <em>→</em> Verifier</h3>\n            <p>Drive our wallet simulator with a <em>target Verifier</em>. Use this to test a wallet against a real Verifier.</p>\n            <div class=\"card-meta\"><span class=\"badge gold\"><span class=\"dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span data-test-count=\"W->V\">— tests</span></span></div>\n          </button>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"section-title\">Dispatch <em>— target &amp; options</em></div>\n        <div class=\"run-panel\">\n          <form class=\"run-form\" id=\"run-form\" autocomplete=\"off\" onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault(); document.getElementById('btn-run').click();\">\n            <label>\n              <span>Mode</span>\n              <select id=\"run-mode\">\n                <option value=\"I->W\">Issuer ↔ Wallet (drive target issuer)</option>\n                <option value=\"V->W\">Verifier ↔ Wallet (drive target verifier)</option>\n                <option value=\"W->I\" selected>Wallet ↔ Issuer (test wallet against target issuer)</option>\n                <option value=\"W->V\">Wallet ↔ Verifier (test wallet against target verifier)</option>\n              </select>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Credential configuration</span>\n              <select id=\"run-credential\"><option>ThaiNationalID</option></select>\n            </label>\n            <label class=\"full\">\n              <span>Target Issuer URL <em class=\"hint-inline\">(leave blank to use built-in mock)</em></span>\n              <input id=\"run-issuer\" type=\"url\" placeholder=\"https://issuer.example.com\" autocomplete=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n            </label>\n            <label class=\"full\">\n              <span>Target Verifier URL <em class=\"hint-inline\">(leave blank to use built-in mock)</em></span>\n              <input id=\"run-verifier\" type=\"url\" placeholder=\"https://verifier.example.com\" autocomplete=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n            </label>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <button id=\"btn-run\" class=\"primary\" type=\"button\">\n                <svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><polygon points=\"3,2 12,7 3,12\"/></svg>\n                <span class=\"btn-label\">Run conformance</span>\n              </button>\n              <button id=\"btn-load-cfg\" class=\"ghost\" type=\"button\">\n                <svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 7h8M7 3l4 4-4 4\"/></svg>\n                Load saved config\n              </button>\n              <span class=\"spacer\"></span>\n              <span class=\"kbd\">or press <kbd>⌘</kbd><kbd>↵</kbd></span>\n            </div>\n          </form>\n          <aside class=\"run-side\" id=\"run-side\" aria-label=\"Run output\">\n            <div class=\"empty\">\n              <svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"4\" width=\"16\" height=\"13\" rx=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M3 8h16M7 12h4\"/></svg>\n              <div>No run yet. Click <strong>Run conformance</strong> above to dispatch the catalog.</div>\n            </div>\n          </aside>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- CONFIG VIEW -->\n      <article class=\"view\" id=\"view-config\" aria-labelledby=\"config-h\">\n        <header class=\"view-header\">\n          <div>\n            <span class=\"eyebrow\">Step 02 · Configure</span>\n            <h2 id=\"config-h\">Configure the <em>default run.</em></h2>\n            <p>Edit the saved run config, manage the wallet's signing keys, and see the environment overrides the container started with.</p>\n          </div>\n        </header>\n        <div class=\"config-grid\">\n          <div class=\"panel\">\n            <div class=\"panel-head\">\n              <h3>Run config</h3>\n              <span class=\"tag\">persisted</span>\n            </div>\n            <form id=\"config-form\">\n              <label>\n                <span>Mode</span>\n                <select name=\"mode\">\n                  <option value=\"I->W\">Issuer ↔ Wallet</option>\n                  <option value=\"V->W\">Verifier ↔ Wallet</option>\n                  <option value=\"W->I\">Wallet ↔ Issuer</option>\n                  <option value=\"W->V\">Wallet ↔ Verifier</option>\n                </select>\n              </label>\n              <label>\n                <span>Default credential configuration</span>\n                <input name=\"credentialConfigurationId\" value=\"ThaiNationalID\" required>\n              </label>\n              <label>\n                <span>Target Issuer URL <em class=\"hint-inline\">(optional)</em></span>\n                <input name=\"targetIssuer\" type=\"url\" placeholder=\"https://issuer.example.com\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n              </label>\n              <label>\n                <span>Target Verifier URL <em class=\"hint-inline\">(optional)</em></span>\n                <input name=\"targetVerifier\" type=\"url\" placeholder=\"https://verifier.example.com\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n              </label>\n              <button class=\"primary\" type=\"submit\">\n                <svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 7l3 3 7-7\"/></svg>\n                Save config\n              </button>\n            </form>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"panel\">\n            <div class=\"panel-head\">\n              <h3>Wallet keys</h3>\n              <span class=\"tag\">in-process</span>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"dim\">Server-generated key pair. Persists only for the lifetime of the server. Regenerate to get a fresh pair.</p>\n            <div id=\"keys-display\" class=\"mono-block\">…</div>\n            <button id=\"btn-regen\" class=\"ghost\" type=\"button\">\n              <svg class=\"icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 14 14\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.5 4.5A5 5 0 1 0 12 8\"/><path d=\"M12 2v3h-3\"/></svg>\n              Regenerate\n            </button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"panel span-2\">\n            <div class=\"panel-head\">\n              <h3>Environment overrides</h3>\n              <span class=\"tag\">read at start</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"mono-block\">\n              <ul>\n                <li><code>PORT</code><span class=\"desc\">listen port (default <code>8080</code>)</span></li>\n                <li><code>HOST</code><span class=\"desc\">listen address (default <code>0.0.0.0</code>)</span></li>\n                <li><code>LOG_LEVEL</code><span class=\"desc\">pino level (default <code>info</code>)</span></li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- HISTORY VIEW -->\n      <article class=\"view\" id=\"view-history\" aria-labelledby=\"history-h\">\n        <header class=\"view-header\">\n          <div>\n            <span class=\"eyebrow\">Step 03 · History</span>\n            <h2 id=\"history-h\">Past <em>runs.</em></h2>\n            <p>Every run is persisted to disk (latest 100). Click a row to open the report in the Run panel. <strong>Shift-click</strong> a row to pin it as the <em>left</em> side of a diff, then click <strong>↔ Diff</strong>.</p>\n          </div>\n        </header>\n        <div id=\"history-list\" class=\"history-list\">\n          <div class=\"empty\" style=\"color:var(--ink-3);font-style:italic;padding:var(--s-3) 0\">No runs yet.</div>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- CATALOG VIEW -->\n      <article class=\"view\" id=\"view-catalog\" aria-labelledby=\"catalog-h\">\n        <header class=\"view-header\">\n          <div>\n            <span class=\"eyebrow\">Step 04 · Catalog</span>\n            <h2 id=\"catalog-h\">Test <em>catalog.</em></h2>\n            <p>Every test case the webapp can execute, with its normative spec reference. Sourced from the corrected Thailand VC OID4VCI / OID4VP 1.0 conformance testcase v2.0.</p>\n          </div>\n        </header>\n        <div id=\"catalog-table\">…</div>\n      </article>\n\n      <!-- ABOUT VIEW -->\n      <article class=\"view\" id=\"view-about\" aria-labelledby=\"about-h\">\n        <header class=\"view-header\">\n          <div>\n            <span class=\"eyebrow\">Step 05 · About</span>\n            <h2 id=\"about-h\">What this is, <em>and what it isn't.</em></h2>\n            <p>A short orientation for first-time users.</p>\n          </div>\n        </header>\n        <div class=\"prose\">\n          <p>The VC Conformance Test Webapp is a self-contained tool for QA engineers who need to verify an <strong>OpenID for Verifiable Credential Issuance 1.0 Final</strong> issuer or an <strong>OpenID for Verifiable Presentations 1.0 Final</strong> verifier — and to verify <em>wallets</em> against real targets.</p>\n          <p>It is <strong>not</strong> a wallet product, a registry, or a trust-list authority. It does not store PII. It does not commit to a real Verifiable Data Registry. It is a <em>test harness</em>.</p>\n          <h3>Cross-modes</h3>\n          <ul>\n            <li><strong>Issuer ↔ Wallet</strong> — drive a target Issuer with our wallet simulator. Use this to verify an Issuer you control. Tests the OID4VCI issuance pipeline (offer → authorization → token → credential).</li>\n            <li><strong>Verifier ↔ Wallet</strong> — drive a target Verifier with our wallet simulator. Use this to verify a Verifier you control. Tests the OID4VP presentation request and response.</li>\n            <li><strong>Wallet ↔ Issuer</strong> — drive our wallet simulator with a target Issuer. Use this to test your wallet against a real Issuer.</li>\n            <li><strong>Wallet ↔ Verifier</strong> — drive our wallet simulator with a target Verifier. Use this to test your wallet against a real Verifier.</li>\n          </ul>\n          <h3>Coverage</h3>\n          <p>The webapp implements the <em>happy-path + canonical negative-path</em> of every operation the spec defines for each role. The current concrete suite is roughly 28 executable test cases covering credential offer, authorization (PKCE + authorization_details), token exchange, credential request (KB-JWT ES256 + EdDSA), deferred credential, notification, and OID4VP DCQL presentation. The number of <em>concrete</em> cases per mode is configurable.</p>\n          <h3>How to read a report</h3>\n          <p>Each row in the report is one test. ✅ means the spec-shaped request was built correctly by our simulator and the target accepted (or rejected, for negative tests). ⏭️ means a prerequisite for that test was not met (e.g. you ran Verifier mode but didn't supply a target verifier). ❌ means the simulator could not build the request per the spec, or the target returned an unexpected error.</p>\n        </div>\n      </article>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <div class=\"toast\" id=\"toast\" hidden role=\"status\" aria-live=\"polite\"></div>\n\n  <script type=\"module\" src=\"/app.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
  }
}